pters, and other crafts used in air transport for the carriage of passengers, goods, mails, and other items. In addition, it acts as commission, booking, indenting, and travel agents; fleet, garage, and service station owners; cargo superintendents and owners; loading and unloading contractors; couriers; liasoners; charters; and package tour operators. Further the company invests, promotes, establishes, administers, and maintains special purpose vehicles. Afcom Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Chennai, India."}}